reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I love this coat! It's warm even on the windy days! It's also light weight and not bulky like some can be. The lining is soft and comfortable (not stiff and scratchy). I've never been a fan of furry collars, but this one isn't bad, and it can be removed if not wanted. The fit is true to size, and I think it looks great. Would certainly recommend if you're looking for warmth and comfort.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality, reasonably priced and delivered fast.
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my 87-year-old mom. She weighs 144lbs and is about 5’ 3”. I purchased a large so she could wear layers underneath. In the photo, she’s wearing a turtleneck, but the coat doesn’t look too big. The lining is soft and will keep her warm. I highly recommend this coat.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Purchased for a friend and was perfect! True to size and was well made and as pretty as picture! Actually looked more expensive. Highly recommended!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice Coat, keeps you warm
reviews.reviewText: Great coat for everyday. I like the coat- the color was exactly as described on the website. The fit was great maybe even a little bit big which is fine with me. The only thing I have a little trouble with sometimes is the zipper. So far it has been okay, but it takes awhile to get the coat zipped up. Other than the issue with the zipper, it is a nice coat for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just as pictured
reviews.reviewText: So I ordered this in a XL, partly because I went by the measurements on their chart and partly because they were out of a 2x, which is what I would have ordered. It does fit however, I like my coats to be a little on the roomy side and sadly it fits a little snug. But, I absolutely LOVE this coat y’all! I ordered the black and it is gorgeous with the gold zipper and snaps etc! The fur lining is beautiful and I’m sure it will be very warm. I’m going to keep it because they still don’t have any more black ones 😕 However, I did go ahead and order the Army green color in a 2x and can’t wait for it to arrive!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute and very warm
reviews.reviewText: I'm happy I went with beige, because I do a lot of walking, and I feel much more visible in the winter bleakness. As others said, good is more for style, as it's huge, with no ties. It is very warm. Only complaint is that it comes very wrinkled and there's nothing you can do but let it hang and gradually fall out.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The style & quality of this nice winter coat is just wonderful! Very true to size, and a super warm & stylish coat for Minnesota winters. The fact you can take the fur trim on & off the hood easily is an added bonus! Could NOT be happier with my purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Fits well but lacks functionality
reviews.reviewText: My wife just purchased one of these coats for the New Year and the reviews are mixed. On the positive side, it's a good looking coat and fits very well, and it's not too thick/not too thin. The inside lining is also very soft, making it extremely comfortable to wear. On the negative side, the complete lack of a drawstring to tighten the ENORMOUS hood was either a glaring oversight or intentionally done to cut corners. There are no side pockets, just the pockets on front that you see in the image. And the two pockets on the chest are fake. Also, the zippers make me nervous.The hunt for a winter coat has gone on for too long so we're throwing in the towel and keeping this one.

reviews.reviewTitle: Great coat and a great price
reviews.reviewText: I really love this coat. Hard to find a fully black coat with black faux fur on the hood, so this was a great find. I am 5'6 and 210lbs and an XL fit perfectly. Jacket length hits mid thigh or so. I can wear a sweater underneath if needed. The adjustable waistline is a great feature and creates a nicer looking fit that isn't bulky and shapeless. The lined inside is super soft and warm. Great pockets on the front, lots of space but doesn't make the coat bulk out too much. Having the options of both a zipper and a button up front allow for nice versatility. Can't beat the price for a great quality coat.

I am 5'3.5" and purchased the medium size. The length of the jacket is perfect, covers down to mid thigh. Very stylish and comfortable. It has a drawstring at the waist to keep the wind out. I wore the coat in a -37c wind and it kept me cozy warm. The only thing missing is a drawstring for the hood. It is quite large and flops around when up. There is a zipper so that the faux trim can be removed. The cuffs are ribbed and are not tight. Overall, I am very satisfied with this purchase.

Absolutely lovely piece. Water resistant and wind proof. Fits like a glove and is true to size. I’m 5’6” and 150 lbs with a larger bust. This jacket is very flattering and very warm. I ordered a large. The gold buttons and ends of draw strings give it that bit more class. Very happy with my purchase! Great value for great quality! Highly recommend.

Looks really good, it’s comfortable and warm. The fur lining on the inside is super soft. All around very happy with my purchase!I ordered a Medium and am 5’4 and about 140lbs. It’s a little loose, so perfect for a sweater and covers my bum.
Nice jacket and was warm and was a perfect fit however the zipper broke after wearing the jacket 3 times I’m rather disappointed
